[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0238","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0105","title":"多款Unix系统 finger 递归查询信息泄露漏洞","description":"finger 服务在处理包含连续 @ 符号的递归查询请求时存在设计缺陷。远程攻击者可通过向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送精心构造的包含多个 @ 符号的长字符串，触发递归查询机制，导致服务资源被过度消耗从而引发拒绝服务，同时也可被用于跨网络用户信息枚举，泄露系统用户名等敏感信息。该漏洞影响大量运行 finger 服务的 UNIX/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0105"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.913","remediation":"建议直接禁用 finger 服务（在 inetd 配置中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd 服务），或在网络防火墙层面阻止 TCP 79 端口的入站与出站流量。若业务必须使用，应升级至支持限制递归查询的 fingerd 实现，或限制可查询的用户列表。现代生产环境建议彻底移除 finger 协议及相关软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0105","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0105"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0336","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0165","title":"Linux Linux 内核 NFS 缓存中毒漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）缓存投毒漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标系统上的 NFS 服务发送特制的 RPC 请求来污染客户端缓存，从而将文件操作重定向至恶意服务器，导致敏感信息泄露、文件篡改乃至任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 SunOS、Solaris 及早期 Linux 发行版中运行的 NFS 服务，CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁加以修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0165"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"1997-03-01","remediation":"在 /etc/exports 中使用完全限定域名（FQDN）替代非限定主机名，避免网组（netgroup）配置歧义。同时建议在服务端升级对应厂商补丁（如 Sun、Red Hat、SUSE 等当时的 NFS 安全更新），并在边界防火墙限制外部对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP、2049/UDP）的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0041","title":"多款Unix系统libc NLS组件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NLS（自然语言服务）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向受影响系统发送特制的 NLS 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 UNICOS 9、MAX 1.3、AIX 4.2、IRIX 6、RedHat 4、Slackware 3、libc 5.2.18 及 mk 1.5 等多个 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。由于涉及系统核心库组件，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0041"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.153","remediation":"对于 Red Hat Linux 4/Slackware 3 等 Linux 系统，应升级至现代发行版并确保 glibc 版本高于 2.0（含 NLS 缓冲区溢出修复）；IBM AIX 4.2 用户请安装 APAR IX70456 补丁或升级至 AIX 5.3 及以上版本；SGI IRIX 6 用户应安装补丁 3369 或升级至 IRIX 6.5.4+。如无法升级，可移除 nls 可执行文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/nls），并限制仅受信用户可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19551","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0041","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0041.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0250","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0109","title":"Sun Solaris ffbconfig 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 的 ffbconfig 图形配置工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 ffbconfig 程序传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统账号才能利用此漏洞实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0109"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.407","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #140 提供的补丁程序，或直接升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/sbin/ffbconfig 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ffbconfig），限制本地非授权用户执行该命令，防止普通用户利用缓冲区溢出提权至 root。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0414","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0228","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RPC Locator 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 RPC Locator 服务（rpcss.exe）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，导致 RPC 定位服务进程崩溃或停止响应，影响系统正常功能。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新解决此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0228"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.410","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对此漏洞发布的热修复补丁 KB Q162567，该补丁解决了 rpcss.exe 在处理特定 RPC 请求时的拒绝服务问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持且不再接收安全更新，建议升级至仍在支持周期内的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：在不需要 RPC Locator 服务的环境中，通过 services.msc 将 Remote Procedure Call (RPC) Locator 服务启动类型设为\"禁用\"，或在防火墙上限制对该服务端口 (TCP 135) 的不必要访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ162567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0228","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0228.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0046","title":"多款Unix系统 rlogin TERM环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rlogin 程序在处理 TERM 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、NeXTstep、SGI IRIX、SunOS 等多种 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0046"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.963","remediation":"针对各受影响系统版本，建议立即升级至修复版本（如 FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、HP-UX 11.00 及以上、IBM AIX 4.2 及以上）；如无法升级，可移除 rlogin 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/rlogin）或禁用 rlogin 服务（注释 inetd.conf 中 login 行并重启 inetd），改用 SSH 替代 rlogin 进行远程登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0046","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19203","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0046","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/622953dc0146a9a48737afdaeb97da06c1b9895d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0494","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0298","title":"SunOS ypbind 路径遍历文件覆盖漏洞","description":"SunOS 与 Linux Slackware 系统中 ypbind 服务在启用 -ypset 或 -ypsetme 选项时存在路径遍历漏洞。远程或本地攻击者可通过构造包含 ..（点点）的特殊请求，绕过目录限制覆盖系统任意文件，导致权限提升或服务异常。该漏洞影响运行 ypbind 且开启上述选项的 SunOS 及 Slackware 系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0298"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.990","remediation":"禁止使用 -ypset 和 -ypsetme 参数启动 ypbind，仅允许通过 ypserv 配置文件（/var/yp/securenets）确定的受信 NIS 服务器绑定。在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 111 和 32770-32800 的外部访问，或禁用 NIS 改用 LDAP 认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/06_ypbindsetme_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0298","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1441/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000146.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0347","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0174","title":"SGI Skunkware 2.0 view-source CGI 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Skunkware 2.0 的 view-source CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感信息泄露，影响 Skunkware 2.0 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0174"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.550","remediation":"立即停止并移除 /cgi-bin/view-source CGI 脚本；如业务需要该功能，重写脚本并对路径参数做严格的输入过滤，拒绝包含 \"../\"、绝对路径或特殊字符的请求；同时在 Web 服务器层面（Apache/Nginx）配置 `AllowOverride None` 和 `Options -Indexes`，并添加访问控制规则阻止对 CGI 目录的未授权访问。由于 Skunkware 2.0 已停止维护多年，建议迁移至较新的操作系统发行版及标准 Web 服务器软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0174","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20568","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0174","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0516","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0516.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0309","title":"HP HP-UX vgdisplay 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 vgdisplay 程序中存在权限分配不当漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该程序以普通用户身份执行 vgdisplay 命令，由于程序未正确限制访问权限，导致攻击者获得 root 级别的系统权限，从而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，需要本地用户账户作为攻击条件。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0309"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.363","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9702-056 中对应的补丁（适用于 HP-UX 10.x 系列）。如无法立即打补丁，可通过 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/vgdisplay 移除 vgdisplay 的 setuid 权限位作为临时缓解措施；同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，仅授予可信用户访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9702-056"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0516.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0607","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0369","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 sdtcm_convert 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中 OpenWindows 环境下的 sdtcm_convert 日历转换工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过向该 setuid 程序传递特制的命令行参数，可触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞需要本地访问权限，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0369"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用 Sun 安全公告 #183 提供的补丁，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本。由于 Solaris 7.0 已停止支持，建议迁移到受支持的 Solaris 版本或替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T13:56:22.329038950+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0129","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0047","title":"Sendmail MIME转换缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"sendmail 8.8.3 及 8.8.4 版本在处理 MIME 邮件编码转换时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标邮件服务器发送特制的 MIME 邮件触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，可能造成服务崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 sendmail 邮件传输代理，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0047"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.130","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.8.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 MIME 转换中的缓冲区溢出问题。若无法立即升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中禁用 MIME 转换功能（O MimeVersion=0）或限制邮件大小作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/685"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0130","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0048","title":"Unix Talkd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Talk 服务守护进程（talkd）在处理 DNS 响应信息时存在输入验证缺陷，当攻击者向目标系统提供特制的恶意 DNS 数据时，可导致缓冲区溢出或命令注入，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多种 UNIX 变种系统（包括 AIX、HP-UX、Solaris 等），攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0048"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.283","remediation":"建议立即禁用 talkd 服务（在 inetd.conf 或 xinetd.d 中注释掉 talk 条目并重启服务），如必须使用应升级至修复该漏洞的版本。同时在边界防火墙上屏蔽 UDP 端口 517（talkd 默认端口），限制对 talk 服务的网络访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/147"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0194","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0081","title":"wu-ftpd RNFR 命令文件覆盖漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd FTP 服务器在实现 FTP 重命名功能时存在路径验证缺陷，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过 FTP 协议发送特制的 RNFR（重命名来源）与 RNTO（重命名为）命令序列，将服务器上的任意文件重写为指定目标文件名，导致文件被覆盖或篡改。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd FTP 服务器，攻击者无需登录认证即可利用匿名 FTP 会话执行操作，成功利用可覆盖系统配置文件或可执行文件，进而可能导致服务异常中断或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0081"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1997-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.170","remediation":"wu-ftpd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 或 Pure-FTPd 等活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件。迁移前，在 /etc/hosts.allow 和防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务仅对可信 IP 段开放，并禁用匿名用户写入权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0081","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0081"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0131","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0049","title":"SGI IRIX Csetup 任意文件创建或覆盖漏洞","description":"IRIX 操作系统中的 Csetup 工具存在任意文件创建或覆写漏洞，由于未对用户输入的文件路径进行充分校验，具有本地访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞创建或覆盖系统关键文件，从而提升权限或导致系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0049"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.417","remediation":"将 IRIX 升级至 6.3 或更高版本；若无法升级，立即移除 Csetup 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/Csetup），并限制不可信用户的本地登录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0049"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0136","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0051","title":"SGI IRIX FLEXlm LicenseManager 任意文件创建与远程代码执行漏洞","description":"FLEXlm LicenseManager（lmgrd）许可管理守护进程 4.0 至 5.0 版本存在文件创建与程序执行漏洞。该漏洞源于 FLEXlm 对用户提交的请求未进行充分校验，导致本地攻击者可利用 lmgrd 进程的权限创建任意文件或执行恶意程序，进而获取目标系统的完全控制权。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 及 Sun Solaris 等多个 Unix 平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此问题，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0051"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.673","remediation":"升级 FLEXlm License Manager 至 5.0 以上版本，或禁用 License Manager 服务。在无法升级的环境下，通过防火墙限制对 lmgrd 端口 (TCP/UDP 27000-27009) 的访问，仅允许受信客户端连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0051","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19350","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml"}]